        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Why do Vegas gates start sagging so fast?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Heat, wind, and slight post movement gang up on them. Once the hinge side goes a little out, the latch end tells on it fast."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can you just replace the latch or hinges?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Sometimes, but on bigger jobs that usually treats the symptom, not the geometry that caused it."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What makes this a high-ticket scope?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
